  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/606890/extras/e68f41aeb2bcc62b4e80cd6f31f1db3a.avif?t=1728650322\" width=616 height=90 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/606890/extras/47632d72ba266d83e08ec3b4c772f30b.avif?t=1728650322\" width=616 height=176 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/606890/extras/d2e303531ea81d3d150f45f5087562c7.poster.avif?t=1728650322\" width=20 height=16 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/606890/extras/d2e303531ea81d3d150f45f5087562c7.webm?t=1728650322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/606890/extras/d2e303531ea81d3d150f45f5087562c7.mp4?t=1728650322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> Masters of Anima is an original adventure game that takes you deep into the magical world of Spark. Battle against the forces of evil in strategic, action-packed battles, where making tactical decisions quickly is vital. Summon and control large armies of up to 100 Guardians, thanks to intuitive and innovative gameplay made from the ground up for controller play, as well as keyboard and mouse.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/606890/extras/80570a4d9e800583da79f7ccb2a1dad8.poster.avif?t=1728650322\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/606890/extras/80570a4d9e800583da79f7ccb2a1dad8.webm?t=1728650322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/606890/extras/80570a4d9e800583da79f7ccb2a1dad8.mp4?t=1728650322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/606890/extras/d2e303531ea81d3d150f45f5087562c7.poster.avif?t=1728650322\" width=20 height=16 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/606890/extras/d2e303531ea81d3d150f45f5087562c7.webm?t=1728650322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/606890/extras/d2e303531ea81d3d150f45f5087562c7.mp4?t=1728650322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <strong>PLAY AS OTTO, AN APPRENTICE OF ANIMA...</strong><br>...gifted with incredible powers and covet the rank of Master to finally marry your betrothed Ana - captive of the terrible Zahr and his fearsome Golems! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/606890/extras/699d0d431fe69c8632df2dca4768c660.poster.avif?t=1728650322\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/606890/extras/699d0d431fe69c8632df2dca4768c660.webm?t=1728650322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/606890/extras/699d0d431fe69c8632df2dca4768c660.mp4?t=1728650322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/606890/extras/d2e303531ea81d3d150f45f5087562c7.poster.avif?t=1728650322\" width=20 height=16 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/606890/extras/d2e303531ea81d3d150f45f5087562c7.webm?t=1728650322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/606890/extras/d2e303531ea81d3d150f45f5087562c7.mp4?t=1728650322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <strong>USE THE POWERS OF ANIMA...</strong><br>...to summon an army of magical Guardians. During your adventure, learn to control new types of Guardians, each with their own unique abilities useful for exploring the world of Spark, as well as for taking down formidable bosses on your way. Acquire new powers for both yourself and your Guardians, and become a true Master of Anima.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/606890/extras/3c27d30ce1bd44ca96516f4c60f709ea.poster.avif?t=1728650322\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/606890/extras/3c27d30ce1bd44ca96516f4c60f709ea.webm?t=1728650322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/606890/extras/3c27d30ce1bd44ca96516f4c60f709ea.mp4?t=1728650322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
